      • regisNum

        RegistrationNumber regisNum()
        Returns the registration number. All cars must have a registration number which uniquely identifies a car.
        返回:
        the registration number

      • refuel

        int refuel(int nfuel)
        Returns how much fuel was added to the tank (which will be 0 if the car is not rented or its tank is already full) Add a given number of whole Liters to the fuel tank. (up to the tank's capacity)
        参数:
        nfuel - the number of whole Liters added to the fuel tank.
        返回:
        how much fuel was added to the tank
        抛出:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if nfuel < 0

      • drive

        int drive(int dist)
        Returns how much fuel was cost by driving a distance.
        参数:
        dist - distance to drive
        返回:
        how much fuel was cost by driving a distance.
